manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Premium Aluminum Shell Double-sided USB C connectors with over-molded strain relief designed for frequent plugging and unplugging, provide a charger cable with reliable performance. Perfect Size and Design A premium Zinc Alloy shell with Anti-slip design for plugging and unplugging. Special Strain Relief design, which makes it have excellent anti-twisting. Nylon Braided Cable Anti-Break Tangle-free Nylon Braided Design. The USB A to USB C Cable is Nylon Braided to add additional durability and tangle free, provide long lifespan.

Stable and Durable This USB C Cable can withstand at least 20000+ cycles of 90-degree bend test. The USB A to USB C Cord built-in 56Ω pull-up resistor and 22AWG thick copper cores to ensure loading safety. Built-in E-Marker Chip The USB A to USB C Cable with E-maker chip inside can quick charge your USB-C devices at up to 3A safe charging power. Charge Samsung S9 from 0 to 70% in 30mins with Qualcomm Quick-Charge 3.0 technology. Standard 56KΩ pull-up resistor provides a safer charging current. So you can experience the charging with total peace of mind. 10Gbps Data Transfer Support up to 10Gbps fast data transfer, connect hard drive and SSD to transfer big files in seconds.

USB A to USB C 3.1 Gen 2 Data Cable & Fast Charging 2 in 1 Cable This USB C Charging Cable can quick charge your USB-C devices at up to 3A safe charging power. Charge Samsung S9 from 0 to 70% in 30mins with Qualcomm Quick-Charge 3.0 technology. Standard 56KΩ pull-up resistor provides a safer charging current. Support up to 10Gbps fast data transfer, connect hard drive and SSD to transfer big files in seconds. Max Output: 20V 3A 60W Material: Aluminum Alloy Cover Date Transfer: USB 3.1 Gen 2 10Gbps Important Notes: This is a USB-A to USB-C Cable, Not USB-C to USB-C Cable. This usb c cord will not provide you with fast charging alone, you will need a power block rated for fast charging and a phone capable of the same. The USB A to USB C Cable can charge for iPhone 15/15 Plus/15 Pro/15 Pro Max and support only 7.5W charging speed for iPhone 15 series. Google pixel is equipped with C-port wall charger in official, so when you use USB A to USB C Cable or the A-port Wall Charger, it can only charge normally but can not support fast charges, because Pixel is using Google’s private charging protocol. If you want to charge quickly, you should use the Pixel original C-port Wall Charger and USB C to USB C Cable. 10 Gbps Data Transfer Support: Transfer data to an external SSD drive with USB-CConnect a USB-C docking station to a host computerTransfer a full-length HD move in less than 30 seconds 60W Super Fast Charging: Built-in E-Marker ChipSupport PD/QC 3.0 fast chargingUp to 60W 20V@3A

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 6, 2024
Reviewed in the United States on January 3, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Works great on older mac with newer hard drive
reviews.reviewText: I needed a cable that would let me attache a newer usb c hard drive to an oldeer iMac. This was nice and long and speed appears to be very good.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 14, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Nice high speed cable
reviews.reviewText: The cable is quite nice. Well made. Fast data transfer. Good length. I use mine mostly with my phone and my portable ssd. Works well for both.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 22, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Not a great connection, comes with an Adapter
reviews.reviewText: Update: This cabel does not have a strong connection when plugging into different devices. I have to try to wiggle it to charge anything. Usually, with a quality connection, you kind of feel a little "click" when plugged in fully. This does not do that, and it hasn't worked for several of my devices that don't flat completely flat. So, it's not as versatile as Id love.This is a nice high quality cable, and it's long enough for some of the most hard to reach outlets. I like that it comes with an extra adapter. The chord is high quality and it charges my phone quickly. I like it!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 30, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars The seller lied about its capacity to transfer data both ways
reviews.reviewText: Before purchasing it I asked the seller a very specific question: did it work in both directions to transfer data, do I need it to connect my Surface Laptop Studio (USB C) to a HUB (USB A), not to charge it?He answered me yes, I bought it, it arrived, I connected it and... it doesn't work in that direction.I'm going to return it. They just wasted my time.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 3, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Works as designed
reviews.reviewText: It works as designed. The build quality is solid and the cable seems very sturdy. The USB C connection is slightly loose, but it works fine even when wiggled and charges as it should.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 19, 2023
reviews.reviewText: This cable has a great build quality and feel. I plugged in my external drive with it, and it is awesome. Much better than the 8" cable that came with the drive!The braided cable seems like it will be very durable. It came with a nice velcro cable tie to keep the cable tidy when not in use.Additionally, it came with an adapter to make the cable usb-c to usb-c. I don't have a need for that at this point, but I imagine it will be handy in the future.As far as cables go, I like this one a lot!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 22, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Needed a longer charging cable to use in my truck with my new iPhone 15 Pro and this thing is nice! I needed the extra length to reach from the USB port in the console, up to the windshield where my phone holder is mounted. This thing disappears whereas the white cable that Apple provides was barely long enough and always got in the way. Anyway, it works like it should, but the nylon braiding really ups the quality. Very happy with this cable!
